<problem id="fs-idp121965760">
<para id="fs-idm103207744">Which of the following figures did <emphasis effect="italics">not</emphasis> actively challenge the status of women in the early American republic?
<list id="fs-idm175543136" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
